<li><p>HS2 progression, cutting journey times between Birmingham and London to 45 minutes and bringing £724million of investment with it.</p></li>

<li><p>Birmingham’s academic reputation; the University of Birmingham is one of the UK’s largest civic universities and most targeted by graduate recruiters. The city is home to five universities in total with a resident student population of 100,000, many of which are foreign students.</p></li>
